4.2. You are getting 502 Bad Gateway error while browsing to one of the production websites. What is your approach to troubleshoot and fix this issue?

5XX errors generally comes from loadbalancers/servers(nginx/httpd/etc).

We can check for below things

1. Check if dns is resolving to correct LB
2. LB is getting proper response from backend servers
3. iptables rules (if particular IPs or ports are blocked)
4.
